<p><strong>Note:</strong> In order to send or receive a fax in Outlook, you must first have a Personal Fax Number. To request a number <a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_9EQfrFfm2qFCr89">click here</a> to fill out the Personal Fax Number Request form.</p>
<ol start="1">
<li><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Open a new e-mail message in Outlook</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span></li>
</ol><ol start="1"><ol start="1">
<li>The fax is addressed using the <strong>To...</strong>line of the email message.&nbsp;<ol>
<li>Simply type <strong>[fax:8</strong> followed by the fax number.</li>
<li>If you are using a <strong>calling card</strong> append that to the end of the number.</li>
<li>End the address with another bracket <strong>]</strong>.<ol>
<li>Examples:&nbsp;<ol>
<li>Campus: <strong>[fax:8</strong>4966511<strong>]</strong></li>
<li>Off Campus (Local): &nbsp;<strong>[fax:8</strong>3561234<strong>]</strong></li>
<li>Off Campus (Toll-Free):<strong> [fax:8</strong>18005281234<strong>]</strong></li>
<li>Off Campus (Calling Card): <strong>[fax:8</strong>18011234567<strong>12345678]</strong></li>
<li>Off Campus (Calling Card - International): <strong>[fax:8</strong>011223344556677<strong>12345678]</strong></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li>The <strong>To, From, Subject</strong>, and message <strong>body</strong> of the email message appear on the cover page of the fax. Fill in this information if you desire it to appear on the cover letter.</li>
</ol></ol>
<p><br />[x50160]</p>
<ol start="1"><ol start="1">
<li>Attach the document you would like to fax by clicking on the <strong>Insert</strong> menu and choosing <strong>File...</strong> or clicking the paper clip icon. <br /><br />Note: Attachments appear as subsequent pages behind the cover letter. <br />
<div align="center"></div>
</li>
</ol></ol>
<p><img height="275" src="Images/helpdesk/email/Send Fax from outlook/fax2.jpg" width="523" /><br /><br /></p>
<ol start="1">
<li>Click <strong>Send</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>If your fax is not delivered successfully, you will receive a notification by e-mail.</p>
<p>To send a test fax use the HP FaxBack Test system by dialing&nbsp;<strong>[fax:8</strong>18884732963<strong>]</strong></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xpowercomponent_Optional Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true" List="xpowercomponent_ContentSnippet"><xPower Type="Component" Component="x50160" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ContentSnippet" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false" Navigation="Ancestors" GenerationOrder="down" StartPage="x5" MaxNodes="" MaxDepth="" Query=""/><xPower Type="Component" Name="SiteControl" l